description: This is a JVM Dashboard for jolokia2 plugin for java

targets.query: SELECT last("uptime") FROM "system" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)
SELECT last("Uptime") FROM "java_runtime" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean("usage_iowait") FROM "cpu" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "cpu" = 'cpu-total') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
